        correlated_data.append(new_energy)

    spot_size = generate_sample('spot_size', intensity, random.choice([np.random.corrcoef(feature1_vals)[0, 1]) if feature2_vals else None)

    generated_data.append([new_target_thickness, np.random.uniform(pulse_width_stats['min'], pulse_width_stats['max']),  # Sample from uniform distribution for pulse width and spot size

# Combine all features into the final dataset
